00:24:00.726 --> 00:24:03.016 A:middle
in color and with specularity.

459
00:24:03.016 --> 00:24:05.076 A:middle
And I'll explain some of
the details of that later.

460
00:24:05.586 --> 00:24:07.476 A:middle
And so we've got
this beautiful image.

